692	2017-04-18 01:46:21	\N	\N	\N	<p>In this episode we continue our series 12 Marks of the Man of God from 1 Timothy 4:6-15. In episode two we looked at the first four marks and in episode four we look at the next four.</p><p>The Man of God:</p><p>5. Disciplines Himself for Godliness (4:7-9)</p><p><span data-offset-key="e4ks5-0-0">6. Is a Hard Worker (4:10)</span></p><p>7. Teaches with Authority (4:11)</p><div><div class="blockIndentSpacer_26b0R"><div class="blockBody_1hxWw clearfix_3EE29 slideOwner_2mt08"><div class="public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr" data-offset-key="e4ks5-0-0">8. Is an Example of Spiritual Maturity (4:12)</div></div></div></div><div class="public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr" data-offset-key="e4ks5-0-0"></div><div class="public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr" data-offset-key="e4ks5-0-0">Be sure to subscribe to the podcast!</div><div class="public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr" data-offset-key="e4ks5-0-0"></div><div class="public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr" data-offset-key="e4ks5-0-0">For more information go to my website <a href="http://nswhitley.com">nswhitley.com</a></div><div class="public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr" data-offset-key="e4ks5-0-0"></div><div><div class="public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr" data-offset-key="e4ks5-0-0">Follow me on Twitter: <a href="http://twitter.com/nswhitley">@nswhitley</a></div><div class="public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr" data-offset-key="e4ks5-0-0"></div><div class="public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr" data-offset-key="e4ks5-0-0">Like and share my Facebook page: <a href="https://www.facebook.com/nswhitley/">https://www.facebook.com/nswhitley/</a></div></div><div class="public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr" data-offset-key="e4ks5-0-0"></div><div class="public-DraftStyle