693	2017-04-03 22:22:26	\N	\N	\N	<p>In this episode we look at what it takes to rightly interpret Scripture. Whether you are a seasoned preacher, a beginner, or simply a student of Scripture who wants to go deeper, then this episode will help you pursue excellence in rightly interpreting Scripture.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><u>Recommended Reading </u></strong></p><p><em>Grasping God’s Word</em> – Duvall and Hayes*</p><p><em>Halley’s Bible Handbook</em>&#8211; Henry H. Halley*</p><p><em>Lectures to my Students</em>&#8211; Charles Spurgeon</p><p><em>Living by the Book</em>&#8211; Howard Hendricks*</p><p><em>How to Read the Bible for All its Worth</em>&#8211; Fee and Stuart*</p><p><em>Biblical Preaching</em>&#8211; Haddon Robinson*</p><p><em>How to Study Your Bible</em>&#8211; Kay Arthur</p><p><em>Discover the Bible for Yourself</em>&#8211; Kay Arthur</p><p><em>The NIV Study Bible- </em>DA Carson (editor)*</p><p><em>The ESV Study Bible*</em></p><p><em>The ESV Student Study Bible</em></p><p>(* <em>highly recommended</em>)</p><p><a href="http://nswhitley.com">nswhitley.com</a></p><p><a href="https://www.facebook.com/nswhitley/">Like and share my Facebook page</a></p><p>Follow me on Twitter: <a href="https://twitter.com/nswhitley">@nswhitley</a><iframe src="https://player.blubrry.com/?media_url=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.blubrry.com%2Fcut_it_straight%2Fcontent.blubrry.com%2Fcut_it_straight%2FSession03.mp3&amp;podcast_link=http%3A%2F%2Fnswhitley.com%2Fcut-it-straight-podcast-episode-003-eight-principles-for-cutting-it-straight%2F#mode-Light&#038;border-000000&#038;progress-000000" scrolling="no" width="100%" height="165" frameborder="0" id="blubrryplayer-71" class="blubrryplayer" title="Blubrry Podcast Player"></iframe></p><p class="powerpress_links powerpress_links_mp3" style="margin-bottom: 1px !important;">Podcast: <a href="http://media.blubrry.com/cut_it_straight/content.blubrry.com/cut_it_straight/Session03.mp3" class="powerpress_link_pinw" target="_blank" title="Play in new